                h2 Typography
                    h3 Helper Classes
                    h4(id="typography-family") Family
                    p Type comes in three families, set by variables in <code class="sg--code-inline">assets/type.css</code>. By default, the <code class="sg--code-inline">body</code> element is set to sans.
                    .sg--example
                        .t--family-serif Serif text
                        .t--family-sans Sans text
                        .t--family-mono Monospace text
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--family-serif&quot;&gt;Serif text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--family-sans&quot;&gt;Sans text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--family-mono&quot;&gt;Monospace text&lt;/div&gt;
                    h4(id="typography-size") Size
                    p Type comes in 5 sizes, set by a <a href="http://www.modularscale.com/">modular scale.</a> The variables that dictate each size are set in <code class="sg--code-inline">assets/type.css</code>.
                    p
                        table
                            thead
                                tr
                                    th Variable
                                    th Description
                                    th Default
                            tbody
                                tr
                                    td <code class="sg--code-inline">--t--base-size</code>
                                    td Base Font Size
                                    td 16px
                                tr
                                    td <code class="sg--code-inline">--ms-base</code>
                                    td Basis for modular scale
                                    td 1rem
                                tr
                                    td <code class="sg--code-inline">--ms-ratio</code>
                                    td Ratio of modular scale sizes
                                    td 1.5
                    .sg--example
                        .t--size-huge Huge text
                        .t--size-xlarge XLarge text
                        .t--size-large Large text
                        .t--size-normal Normal text
                        .t--size-small Small text
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--size-huge&quot;&gt;Huge text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--size-xlarge&quot;&gt;XLarge text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--size-large&quot;&gt;Large text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--size-normal&quot;&gt;Normal text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--size-small&quot;&gt;Small text&lt;/div&gt;
                    h4(id="typography-weight") Weight
                    p Type comes in 3 weights, set by the variables in  <code class="sg--code-inline">assets/type.css</code>.
                    .sg--example
                        .t--weight-bold Bold text
                        .t--weight-normal Normal text
                        .t--weight-light Light text
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--weight-black&quot;&gt;Black text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--weight-bold&quot;&gt;Bold text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--weight-normal&quot;&gt;Normal text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--weight-light&quot;&gt;Light text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--weight-thin&quot;&gt;Thin text&lt;/div&gt;
                    h4(id="typography-alignment") Alignment
                    p Alignment can be set using one of three helper classes.
                    .sg--example
                        .t--align-left Left-aligned text
                        .t--align-center Center-aligned text
                        .t--align-right Right-aligned text
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--align-left&quot;&gt;Left-aligned text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--align-center&quot;&gt;Center-aligned text&lt;/div&gt;
                            &lt;div class=&quot;t--align-right&quot;&gt;Right-aligned text&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                    h3 Elements
                    h4(id="typography-headings") Headings
                    p Headings 1-4 are available as shorthand for commonly-used size, weight, and color styles. Feel free to style these as you wish.
                    .sg--example
                        h1 Heading 1
                        h2 Heading 2
                        h3 Heading 3
                        h4 Heading 4
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;h1&gt;Heading 1&lt;/h1&gt;
                            &lt;h2&gt;Heading 2&lt;/h2&gt;
                            &lt;h3&gt;Heading 3&lt;/h3&gt;
                            &lt;h4&gt;Heading 4&lt;/h4&gt;
                    h4(id="typography-paragraphs") Paragraphs
                    p Paragraph text is styled at the <code class="sg--code-inline">body</code> level, with the exception of the addition of <code class="sg--code-inline">margin-bottom: 1rem</code> for <code class="sg--code-inline">&lt;p&gt;</code> tags.
                    .sg--example
                        p Paragraph Text. We work with clients as partners and collaborators on the way to a shared goal. While projects vary and methods evolve, our work is always characterized by a commitment to a few fundamentals.
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;p&gt;&#10;Paragraph Text. We work with clients as partners and collaborators &#10;on the way to a shared goal. While projects vary and methods evolve, &#10;our work is always characterized by a commitment to a few fundamentals.&#10;&lt;/p&gt;
                    h4(id="typography-lists") Lists
                    p By default, <code class="sg--code-inline">&lt;ul&gt;</code> is styled with bullets and <code class="sg--code-inline">&lt;ol&gt;</code> is styled with numerals. Additionally, there is a <code class="sg--code-inline">t--list-unstyled</code> helper class to remove styling from any list.
                    .sg--example
                        ul
                            li Unordered list
                            li Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
                            li Consectetur adipiscing elit
                            ul
                                li Nested list
                                li Consectetur adipiscing elit
                                li Integer molestie lorem at massa
                            li Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
                            li Consectetur adipiscing elit
                            li Integer molestie lorem at massa
                        ol
                            li Ordered List
                            li Consectetur adipiscing elit
                            li Integer molestie lorem at massa
                        ul.t--list-unstyled
                            li Unstyled List
                            li Consectetur adipiscing elit
                            li Integer molestie lorem at massa
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;ul&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Unordered list&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Consectetur adipiscing elit&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;ul&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;Nested list&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;Consectetur adipiscing elit&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;Integer molestie lorem at massa&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;/ul&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Consectetur adipiscing elit&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Integer molestie lorem at massa&lt;/li&gt;
                            &lt;/ul&gt;
                            &lt;ol&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Ordered List&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Consectetur adipiscing elit&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Integer molestie lorem at massa&lt;/li&gt;
                            &lt;/ol&gt;
                            &lt;ul class=&quot;t--list-unstyled&quot;&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Unstyled List&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Consectetur adipiscing elit&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li&gt;Integer molestie lorem at massa&lt;/li&gt;
                            &lt;/ul&gt;
                    h4(id="typography-blockquotes") Block Quotes
                    p The <code class="sg--code-inline">&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> element is styled simply to provide differentiation from text.
                    .sg--example
                        blockquote Planetary helps us design, counsel, and build products for our and our clients' future.
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;blockquote&gt;
                                Planetary helps us design, counsel, and build
                                products for our and our clients&apos; future.
                            &lt;/blockquote&gt;
                    h4(id="typography-code") Code
                    p Preformated text and code can be styled using the <code class="sg--code-inline">&lt;pre&gt;</code> and <code class="sg--code-inline">&lt;code&gt;</code> tags.
                    .sg--example
                        pre Preformatted text
                        code Code text
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;pre&gt;Preformatted text&lt;/pre&gt;
                            &lt;code&gt;Code text&lt;/code&gt;
