                    h2 Tables
                    p Tables are styled with the fewest elements possible. For more styling, including text alignment and color, use helper classes. For guidelines on how to style tables, read <a href="https://medium.com/mission-log/design-better-data-tables-430a30a00d8c#.od49lsyoa">Design Better Data Tables</a>.
                    .sg--example
                        table
                            thead
                                tr
                                    th Flavor
                                    th.t--align-right Inventory
                                    th.t--align-right Sales
                            tbody
                                tr
                                    td Vanilla
                                    td.t--align-right 120
                                    td.t--align-right $300.23
                                tr
                                    td Chocolate
                                    td.t--align-right 20
                                    td.t--align-right 203.39
                                tr
                                    td Pistachio
                                    td.t--align-right 139
                                    td.t--align-right 192.29
                    pre.sg--code
                        code.html.
                            &lt;table&gt;
                                &lt;thead&gt;
